data.text:
About 1233 S 2240 E

This stunning home, built in 2017, located in the beautiful Heber Valley offers the convenience of main floor living and has been lovingly updated throughout. With 7 bedrooms and 5+ bathrooms, there's plenty of space for everyone. We've added a fantastic theater area for movie nights and created ample gathering spots for family and friends. Situated on 1.18 acres, the property features a large garage, a spacious outdoor patio with a gas fire pit and hot tub, and incredible views of Timpanogas Mountain. Whether you're headed downtown or to the mountains, everything is just minutes away. Come see why this could be your forever home!
